sentences: Mohammad Kautsar Hikmat (born October 5, 1981), known professionally as Uki Noah, is an Indonesian guitarist who is best known as the rhythm guitarist of the pop band Noah for 19 years.
The family moved to Australia in 1989 and stayed for four years.
In 2009, Uki married a soap opera actress, Metha Yunatria.
They have one child, and lost a second child shortly after birth, in July 2015.

Mohammad Kautsar Hikmat (born October 5, 1981), known professionally as Uki Noah, is an Indonesian guitarist who is best known as the rhythm guitarist of the pop band Noah for 19 years.
